casebody.data:
LAMBERT, Appellant, v. CARR et al., Respondents. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. May 11, 1894.) Action by Henry A. Lambert against George W. Carr and others.

Argued before DALY, C. J., and BOOKSTAVER and PRYOR, JJ.

Wm. A. Abbott, for appellant. Cantor & Van Schaiek, for respondents.

No opinion. Ordered that the order be reversed, with costs.
